OL,6,FEir and Ryanair have generated the
OL,7,Fmost complaints and customer queries
OL,8,Fof all businesses in Ireland,
OL,9,Faccording to data from the state
OL,10,Fconsumer watchdog.
OL,12,FQueries and complaints to the
OL,13,FCompetition and Consumer Protection
OL,14,FCommission increased by 18% in the
OL,15,Ffirst six months of 2024 compared with
OL,16,Fthe same period last year.
OL,18,FA total of 22,347 people contacted the
OL,19,FCCPC helpline between January and June
OL,20,Ffor free information on their consumer
OL,21,Frights and support on personal finance.
