OL,6,FConsumer electronics firm Harvey
OL,7,FNorman was in fifth place on 234.
OL,9,FGrainne Griffin, CCPC director of
OL,10,Fcommunications, said: "Whether you're
OL,11,Fbuying a birthday card or a brand-new
OL,12,Fcar, you have rights as a consumer,
OL,13,Fand the trader you're buying from has
OL,14,Fcertain responsibilities under the law.
