OL,6,F"It can be tricky for consumers to
OL,7,Funderstand their rights when something
OL,8,Fbreaks down or a delivery doesn't show
OL,9,Fup, and that's where the CCPC can
OL,10,Fhelp. An informed consumer is an
OL,11,Fempowered consumer, and knowing your
OL,12,Frights can make life easier when
OL,13,Fthings go wrong.
OL,15,F"Traders who break the law can face
OL,16,Ffines and prosecution. Our enforcement
OL,17,Fofficers use this helpline data to
OL,18,Fidentify serious breaches of the law
OL,19,Fand patterns of non-compliance."
