OL,6,FIn total, 4,900 consumers were
OL,7,Freferred to the Small Claims Court,
OL,8,Falmost 1,000 more than during the same
OL,9,Fperiod in 2023.
OL,11,FTopping the list of sectors most
OL,12,Freferred to the court were home
OL,13,Fbuilding and improvements, with 624
OL,14,Fconsumers referred, and vehicles and
OL,15,Ftransport, with 588.
OL,17,FMs Griffin said changes to the law are
OL,18,Frequired to give the CCPC the "power
OL,19,Fto impose larger fines for serious
OL,20,Foffences", such as a percentage of a
OL,21,Fbusiness's turnover.
